{"tid":2419263,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★安心出行下載量被質疑　揭網購平台買賣like產業　最平$25有交易","createTime":"2021-02-23T08:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T08:26:49.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"28983bfba43fc212594a76a0cb4d5d480ed3ec25","tid":2419263,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210223/440888159962664960416823.jpeg/sUPFN1LUhxxla-RreUNkxSrzzUGDrvRbO34yhjt-MoY?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210223%2F440888159962664960416823.jpeg%2FsUPFN1LUhxxla-RreUNkxSrzzUGDrvRbO34yhjt-MoY%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=62530752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《香港01》記者於1個拍賣平台搜尋「買like」資料，發現相關買賣的目標平台可分為facebook、instagram以及YouTube；「產品」則主要分為讚好（追蹤）、留言及直播觀眾3類。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210223/440869632652349440318762.png/cWFAOzqg9uwJh_JTViZbgIZXWooquwrymhox1poaMdY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210223%2F440869632652349440318762.png%2FcWFAOzqg9uwJh_JTViZbgIZXWooquwrymhox1poaMdY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=1f65e785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFacebook及instagram的讚好及追蹤屬最普遍的「商品」，只要付出約50元，即可獲得100個讚好，數量愈多價錢愈平，750元已能購入5000讚好。部分公司更提供進一步選擇，買家能揀選指定國家如華人或韓國「粉絲」，以免出現大量非洲粉絲讚好本地帳戶的明顯造假情況。賣家更強調，「增粉過程完全保密」，並提供貼士建議想成為KOL的帳戶「買followers」，網店則應「買like」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/590377/%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89%E9%87%8F%E8%A2%AB%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91-%E6%8F%AD%E7%B6%B2%E8%B3%BC%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E8%B2%B7%E8%B3%A3like%E7%94%A2%E6%A5%AD-%E6%9C%80%E5%B9%B3-25%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F590377%2F%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25B8%